The paper discusses the impact of hardware impairments on a massive MU-MIMO system, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), and system engineering (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper involves simulations and modeling of antenna arrays (cs.MM) and discusses the effects on the modulated RF signal (cs.AR).
